Package: MGS
Type: Package
Title: Matrix Game Solver
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matej", "Novak", email = "matej.novak3@student.ukf.sk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    A collection of functions for analyzing and solving two-player zero-sum matrix games. 
    Includes support for saddle point detection, dominated strategy elimination, solving diagonal and 
    square matrices, graphical 2-by-n game solutions and pivoting algorithm for solving matrix games.
